            "text": "<p>Honiture robotic vacuum cleaner series combines intelligent navigation with powerful suction to provide hands-free cleaning for your home. Equipped with smart sensors, multiple cleaning modes, and anti-tangle brushes, the cleaning vacuum robot effortlessly tackle dust, pet hair, and debris on all floor types. With scheduled cleaning and automatic recharging, they make maintaining a clean and tidy home easier than ever.<\/p>",
